&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Role Summary&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Accounting Manager will own the month-end close and general ledger accounting operations for Alpha Lion. In this role, you will execute close tasks with precision, maintain accurate and well-documented GL records, and continuously improve accounting processes to support a fast-growing business. You will collaborate closely with cross-functional teams across time zones and serve as a key contributor to the Finance team&#39;s ability to deliver accurate, timely financial reporting to leadership.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own and execute month-end close tasks including journal entries, account reconciliations, transaction coding, and financial statement preparation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain GL accuracy and ensure all entries are properly supported and audit-ready&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Complete recurring weekly accounting tasks such as data sync monitoring, transaction processing, and report maintenance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and implement process improvements that increase efficiency and accuracy in financial reporting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with cross-functional teams on ad hoc projects including ERP improvements, data flows, and tax preparation support&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What Success Looks Like&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Month-end close tasks are completed on time with clean reconciliations and minimal rework&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;GL records are accurate, well-documented, and immediately reviewable&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Process improvements are proactively identified and implemented&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Internal and external stakeholders receive clear, proactive, and timely communication&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who You Are&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You take full ownership of your work, meet deadlines consistently, and communicate proactively when issues arise&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You track everything, assume nothing, and take pride in documentation that speaks for itself&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are a natural systems thinker who is always looking for ways to streamline and improve&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You thrive in a remote, international environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Experience &amp;amp; Skills&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;4+ years of accounting experience with direct ownership of month-end close and GL accounting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;NetSuite proficiency preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with ecommerce or small/medium US companies preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor&#39;s degree in Accounting, Finance, or related field; CPA or equivalent is a plus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication skills in English; comfortable working with global teams across time zones&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Compensation&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2,500~$2,800 USD/month. Offer will reflect experience, skill set, and local market alignment.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Creative Strategist&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Role Summary&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’re looking for a &lt;strong&gt;highly performance-driven Creative Strategist &lt;/strong&gt;to own the development of high-performing paid social creative that drives profitable customer acquisition at scale.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this role, you will translate &lt;strong&gt;consumer psychology&lt;/strong&gt;, product truth, and performance data into &lt;strong&gt;scalable creative systems&lt;/strong&gt; that educate, persuade, and convert. You’ll own creative strategy from research and ideation through testing, iteration, and scaling — &lt;strong&gt;partnering closely with designers, editors, creators, media buyers, and production teams&lt;/strong&gt; to continuously unlock growth opportunities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This is not a brand-awareness role.&lt;/strong&gt; We are looking for someone who understands direct response creative and can consistently build winning ads that drive &lt;strong&gt;revenue, &lt;/strong&gt;especially across&lt;strong&gt; Meta.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Develop and execute creative strategies&lt;/strong&gt; that drive profitable customer acquisition across paid social channels, primarily Meta.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Research customers deeply&lt;/strong&gt; to identify pain points, buying motivations, objections, awareness levels, and scalable creative opportunities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Build and continuously test new creative concepts&lt;/strong&gt;, hooks, angles, and messaging to prevent fatigue and improve efficiency.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Own the development of clear, high-signal creative briefs&lt;/strong&gt; for designers, creators, influencers, editors, and production partners.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Lead structured creative testing and iteration&lt;/strong&gt; by analyzing performance signals and evolving winning concepts to maximize scale.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Conduct competitive and market research&lt;/strong&gt; to identify emerging trends, high-performing formats, and best-in-class DTC creative.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Partner cross-functionally&lt;/strong&gt; with media buyers, production teams, post-production, creators, and marketing stakeholders to maintain a fast and efficient creative pipeline.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What Success Looks Like&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Successfully helping scale acquisition funnels through high-performing creative while maintaining profitability targets.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identifying and scaling multiple winning creative angles that sustain performance and reduce creative fatigue.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Operating a high-velocity creative testing engine with strong organization, iteration, and learning systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Developing diversified creative across audiences, personas, hooks, formats, and creators to support long-term growth.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who You Are:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You deeply understand consumer psychology and enjoy figuring out what actually makes people buy.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are performance-first and care about business outcomes, not just creative aesthetics.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You move quickly, embrace testing, and adapt fast when data signals change.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You take ownership and proactively solve problems before performance declines.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You combine creative intuition with analytical rigor and enjoy turning insights into repeatable systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You thrive in fast-paced environments with high output expectations and constant iteration.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Experience &amp;amp; Skills:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;u

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Role Summary&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’re looking for a &lt;strong&gt;highly analytical&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;performance-driven&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;strong&gt;Growth Marketer &lt;/strong&gt;to own &lt;strong&gt;paid acquisition execution and scaling&lt;/strong&gt; across &lt;strong&gt;Meta&lt;/strong&gt;, Google, and other assigned channels. In this role,&lt;strong&gt; you will manage high-volume ad spend&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;optimize acquisition funnels&lt;/strong&gt;, and &lt;strong&gt;turn performance insights&lt;/strong&gt; into actionable growth opportunities. You’ll partner closely with Growth, Creative, and CRO teams to improve customer acquisition efficiency, scale winning strategies, and drive measurable business impact.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is an ideal role for someone who thrives in&lt;strong&gt; fast-paced direct response environments&lt;/strong&gt;, loves testing and optimization, and combines strong platform expertise with a deep understanding of business performance.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own day-to-day campaign management across Meta, Google, TikTok, and assigned acquisition channels.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Execute daily optimizations including scaling, budget allocation, creative rotations, audience testing, and campaign structure improvements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Launch and manage structured creative testing initiatives across hooks, angles, offers, landing pages, and audience strategies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct weekly performance analysis to identify trends, risks, inefficiencies, and scaling opportunities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate campaign and funnel insights into actionable recommendations for creative strategy, CRO, offers, and acquisition performance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain high standards of account organization, QA, reporting accuracy, tracking, and operational documentation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay ahead of platform updates, algorithm changes, and paid media best practices to continuously improve execution quality.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What Success Looks Like&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You consistently scale paid acquisition while maintaining efficiency and profitability targets.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You proactively identify performance opportunities and problems before they become major issues.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your reporting and analysis lead to stronger creative decisions, improved funnel performance, and better business outcomes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Campaign execution is highly organized, detail-oriented, and follows disciplined operational processes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who You Are:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You take ownership and accountability for results.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You move fast, adapt quickly, and make strong decisions with imperfect information.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are highly analytical and enjoy connecting performance data to business outcomes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have exceptional attention to detail and maintain high operational standards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You enjoy testing, experimentation, and continuously improving performance systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You communicate clearly and proactively, ensuring strong visibility into performance and learnings.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Experience &amp;amp; Skills:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;4+ years of hands-on experience managing paid acquisition campaigns across &lt;strong&gt;Meta,&lt;/strong&gt; Google, and/or TikTok.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven experience managing &lt;strong&gt;$1M+ monthly ad spend&lt;/strong&gt; in a direct response or DTC environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong understanding of attribution, acquisition funnels, creative testing frameworks, and performance measurement.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High proficiency with Excel/Goo

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This is a remote role and can be based in:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Remote, United States: W2 position&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
